{"tid":2494373,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"一條關於Array既問題","createTime":"2021-04-18T14:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T14:41:13.000Z","uid":257658,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2893d601a453c50978ceabee01e18f2c44294aff","tid":2494373,"uid":257658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:24:51.000Z","msg":"是咁的. 我用C++寫緊個Inventory System.<br />\n好似生化危機咁樣. 可以inspect, use item, drop item... etc.<br />\nInventory用一條array儲著.<br />\n科興就係Inventory[0], inventory[1],[2],[3] ....<br />\nExample: <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRUAFJKE5Svn31Uvj3gEBR4UvugY8u7bhZzmXzGZSBmVC?filename=baYvjXb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbaYvjXb.png&h=bc31dca5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原本隻驚<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaUFQ4XQV1emt8L1J47AbmiCmBfaYzm3UKLLWeze3kTa1?filename=KEJbOPW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKEJbOPW.png&h=16ecc58e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本來都就黎寫完. 但岩岩玩玩RE Village先唸起.<br />\nItem既位置可以隨意調換. <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/unexpected.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.<br />\n但點樣做到佢上下左右調Item果個效果?<br />\nE.g. GIF:<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWgsVjZg8rvd8DuDznUWkJyEtNBRiQsBArbw2LoVmEmn1?filename=8coZXHE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8coZXHE.gif&h=79f90471&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n定係我既approach已經係錯左? 原本隻驚唔係用array儲inventory item?"},{"pid":"8f20ba6131456830324f652ffe95c019f6072b90","tid":2494373,"uid":46200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:33:17.000Z","msg":"就咁swap 未得？有咩特別？"},{"pid":"1f353ba826e07e7957feb4bf9b6112913c30e076","tid":2494373,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:34:26.000Z","msg":"用pointer"},{"pid":"13e8e3704428230b791bf567f0aa967b2eaab4e6","tid":2494373,"uid":125017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:35:14.000Z","msg":"唔抄VALVE啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669cecc608222e8591622d09b62bd8f1f7f02454","tid":2494373,"uid":379900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:37:28.000Z","msg":"唔係就咁swap咋咩<br />\n2d array A裝住，swap A[i, j]同A[i',  j']時求其搵個tmp = A[i, j], 跟住A[i, j]  = A[i', j'],  A[i', j'] = tmp"},{"pid":"b00bd0acfba6a4050edcfc56cd8502601a740058","tid":2494373,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:38:56.000Z","msg":"好想同樓主做愛"},{"pid":"4b1567275d289a14e5ba9eabe612faa5b2e4c089","tid":2494373,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:39:55.000Z","msg":"用2D array?"},{"pid":"870fc553d066a330d80aa9fc2233281da40ef84a","tid":2494373,"uid":118286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f20ba6131456830324f652ffe95c019f6072b90","tid":2494373,"uid":46200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:33:17.000Z","msg":"就咁swap 未得？有咩特別？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:41:13.000Z","msg":"我覺得個問題係樓主想用keyboard 控制個swap<br />\n響個1Darray點知下一行同一格嘅index係咩<br />\n答案:用2D array"}]}